Interface Commit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Signable
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface Commit
extends Signable
    Allows access to information about a transaction that is committed to the ledger.

      • getStatus

        org.hyperledger.fabric.protos.peer.TransactionPackage.TxValidationCode getStatus()
